{"tid":1663834,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《有感而發》 香港人聽日見！","createTime":"2019-10-19T16:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T16:12:25.000Z","uid":177554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db0829bd99088bb25991e1e2e4a1e44cc4f0b1f0","tid":1663834,"uid":177554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:11:10.000Z","msg":"藍/紅既人我都可以當係政見唔同。<br />\n<br />\n我想講有啲人開口埋口話自己香港人,  去外國讀書會話homesick，去旅行回程會講finally home / home kong。<br />\n<br />\n但當你屋企既核心價值俾人挑戰緊，需要你企出黎一齊抵抗，就個個影都唔見聲都唔出。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢類人只係口裡話自己係香港一分子, 心入面根本唔Care香港既情況。去到第二個國家生活照可以臉不紅氣不喘講Nowhere better than home 呢d說話。<br />\n<br />\nFine! Then don&rsquo;t abuse the word &ldquo;香港人&rdquo;.  你頂多係citizen in hk. You are never one of us. <br />\n<br />\n你永遠唔會有我地呢班唔願意走，守護香港到底既人果種歸屬感。香港對於真正既香港人黎講係唯一既屋企。<br />\n<br />\n香港既文化自由法治我地自己守護！ 香港人聽日見！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SvnJj50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSvnJj50.jpg&h=c6ef45e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G5TAbdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG5TAbdd.jpg&h=c31bba2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c707f0246dfd5c8fa1a40281ae33f43c3082f6b7","tid":1663834,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:11:23.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f45b8075299acd35f81b78d566d16e70a1935836","tid":1663834,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:12:25.000Z","msg":"90後勇武：有螢光帶但我哋唔係鬼 香港人反抗冇得再輸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1663823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1663823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}